40:40.630 --> 40:42.170
And that's cheap, really.

40:42.170 --> 40:44.470
Did you just say "that's cheap"?
That's what you said.

40:44.470 --> 40:47.040
$250,000.
That's a little rich.

40:47.040 --> 40:48.610
No, I'm<i> big</i> richard.

40:48.610 --> 40:50.710
We can bargain a little, or you
