41:30.580 --> 41:32.920
Daggum, now you're
selling the salesman.

41:32.920 --> 41:34.190
Come on. Come on,
come on.

41:34.190 --> 41:35.550
-Alright, $200,000 it is, man.
-That's fine.

41:35.560 --> 41:38.220
Right on. Kick-ass. That's
really cool for gas monkey.

41:38.230 --> 41:39.490
Wait till
the crew finds out.

41:39.490 --> 41:41.260
Well, it wasn't the $250,000
that I wanted,

41:41.260 --> 41:43.500
