41:45.470 --> 41:47.230
and gas monkey wins again.

41:47.230 --> 41:49.530
One-of-a-kind.
Finished, done, sold.

41:49.540 --> 41:50.800
See ya next time!

41:50.800 --> 41:52.940
You're getting a good deal.
